<br>
&quot;So be it&quot; Sighed Vulak'Aerr, shaking his head in discontent. &quot;If that is your wish,  you are well aware of the consequences&quot;. Vulak'Aerr turned his look upon the elders in the room and noded slowly. The reflection of the torches in his eyes became clearer as they began to moisten. <br>
<br>
The shackled form remained still as the judgement was passed upon him. <br>
<br>
A dark silence descended upon the majestic dome shaped room. Chants began to echo throughout the hallways as the elders began conjuring an ancient spell. Never had this spell been used upon one of their own, never had one of their own betrayed the circle of elders.<br>
<br>
The shackled form began to hurl in pain, torrential pain. His once massive form was shrinking, his limbs becoming shorter. His golden scales melting into a uniform surface, turning into a somewhat pinkish in color. <br>
<br>
Vulak'Aerr turned away from the transformation. &quot;I have lost some of my kind through warfare, but never have I lost one because of infatuation. You are a disgrace to our kind, you have betrayed us for the last time. You are being stripped of all magical powers, poor fool.&quot;<br>
<br>
Screams of unheard pain echoed throughout the realm. What seemed to be the screeching cry of a dragon was now the wailing of a human voice. Every resident bowed their heads in respect to the loss and continued on about their business.<br>
<br>
&quot;You will now live the undignified life of the race you loved most, humans.&quot; Vulak'Aerr muttered a word now incoherent to the human.<br>
<br>
The cries stopped abruptly, as the human fell to the ground. Too weak to move the human lay lifeless on the bitter cold marble floor. With his last shred of stamina he opened his eyes, but even that was too demanding. <br>
<br>
&quot;Let it known from this day forth&quot; said Vulak'Aerr. &quot;Harve'cha is now a fallen dragon soul&quot;.<br>
<br>
Vulak'Aerr looked at the human form for the last time and snarled with disgust. &quot;Send him to where he now belongs...&quot;<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
