<br>
Upon arriving at the bakery, Phallen was starving. The bakery smell was strong and was mouth watering. <br>
<br>
&quot;Ye want a cookie sir?&quot; Asked a tiny female voice.<br>
<br>
&quot;huh?&quot; <br>
<br>
&quot;I said.. Ye want a cookie sir?&quot; She asked again.<br>
<br>
&quot;That is not what I come here for.&quot; Phallen replied evading a direct answer for he knew that he really wanted some of that bakery.<br>
<br>
A little hand popped up on the table and then a little halfling face followed. She was rather pretty for a halfling, nice little chubby cheeks, and short stubby hands. &quot;If you don't want my cookies.. then what might you want?&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;I am looking for guidance.&quot; he replied.<br>
<br>
&quot;Ahhhhh... well then.. cookies are just what you need!&quot; The little blonde haired halfling looked around the table, &quot;Now, where did I put that guidance cookie?&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;I am sorry, I must have you confused with someone else,&quot; bowed Phallen as he started to walk backwards.<br>
<br>
&quot;Don't go anywhere! I will find that cookie and you will eat it, and all will fall into place.&quot; <br>
<br>
&quot;How is a cookie supposed to bring me guidance, ridiculous really.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Because my name is Andlie, and when I say you eat my cookies.. you eat my cookies. Got it?&quot; snarled Andlie.<br>
&quot;But, M'a...&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;No!&quot; She raised her little arm in the air, &quot; I don't want to hear you till you eat my cookie!&quot;<br>
<br>
A moment of silence grew between Phallen and Andlie. Phallen wasn't sure if he should make a run for the nearest street and get away form the crazed baker, or stay and be told what to do. <br>
<br>
&quot;Ah!, I found it.. &quot; exclaimed Andlie, &quot;Eat this and you will understand&quot;<br>
<br>
Andlie handed Phallen a flattened hard as rock cookie. Not knowing how to go about eating it without breaking his teeth he reluctantly took a small bite from it. A sour taste ran through his mouth, and his cheeks puckered instantly. Trying to keep the look of disgust from showing he smiled while pretending to chew on a much bigger piece of cookie than he really had.<br>
<br>
&quot;Mmmmmm.. quite tasty!&quot; Said Phallen.<br>
<br>
&quot;Now come with me, hurry we don't have a great deal of time&quot; She told him showing him the back door the the tent.<br>
<br>
&quot;Where are we going?&quot; <br>
<br>
&quot;For guidance moron!&quot;<br>
<br>
